detectors.description: DODOPool.swap(address,address,uint256) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#64-101) ignores return value by IERC20(toToken).transfer(maintainer,fee) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#98)

DODOPool.swap(address,address,uint256) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#64-101) performs a multiplication on the result of a division:
	- toAmount = (baseBalance * fromAmount) / (quoteBalance + fromAmount) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#85)
	- fee = (toAmount * lpFeeRate) / 10000 (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#91)

	External calls:
	- IERC20(fromToken).transferFrom(msg.sender,address(this),fromAmount) (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#77)
	State variables written after the call(s):
	- baseBalance += fromAmount (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#82)
	- baseBalance -= toAmount (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#87)
	- quoteBalance -= toAmount (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#83)
	- quoteBalance += fromAmount (samples/tc/minimalsanitized/contracts_cleaned/ms_tc_018.sol#86)
